ENTRY            D1083   20260216   20260508   20260508       D151
SUBENT        D1083001   20260216   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                 12         28
TITLE      Study of the 7Li+154Sm inelastic reaction using
            particle-gamma coincidences
AUTHOR     (F.Ramirez, D.A.Torres, J.R.B.Oliveira, N.H.Medina,
            A.S.Serra, V.A.B.Zagatto)
INSTITUTE  (3BZLIPE,3BZLUFF)
           (3CLMCLM) Universidad Nacional de Colombia, Bogota
REFERENCE  (J,EPJ/A,61,216,2025)
FACILITY   (VDGT,3BZLUSP)
SAMPLE     154Sm target with a thickness of 97 ug/cm2.
DETECTOR   (SCIN) LYSO crystal arrays, each with 3 X 3
            scintillation crystals, were used for gamma-ray
            detection. Each crystal has a length of 40 mm and
            covers an area of 12.4 X 12.4 mm2. The arrays (LYSO A
            at 90 degree and LYSO B at 180 degree) were placed
            55 mm from the target.
           (TELES) The phoswich scintillator telescope consists of
            a 0.1 mm thick fast scintillation detector delta E
            for detecting 7Li, bonded to a 10 mm thick long decay
            time E detector.
METHOD     (EDE)
           (COINC) The particle-gamma coincidence technique has
            been used because low-lying states of 154Sm are too
            close to the ground state, making it difficult to
            separate the individual cross sections.
PART-DET   (G,3-LI-7)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on sources of uncertainties
STATUS     (TABLE,,F.Ramirez+,J,EPJ/A,61,216,2025) Table 2
HISTORY    (20260216C) VT
ENDBIB              28
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           31
SUBENT        D1083002   20260216   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                  3          9
REACTION   (62-SM-154(3-LI-7,INL)62-SM-154,PAR,DA)
EN-SEC     (E-LVL1,3-LI-7)
           (E-LVL2,62-SM-154)
LEVEL-PROP (3-LI-7,E-LVL1=0.000,SPIN=1.5,PARITY=-1.)
           (3-LI-7,E-LVL1=0.478,SPIN=0.5,PARITY=-1.)
           (62-SM-154,E-LVL2=0.000,SPIN=0.,PARITY=+1.)
           (62-SM-154,E-LVL2=0.082,SPIN=2.,PARITY=+1.)
           (62-SM-154,E-LVL2=0.267,SPIN=4.,PARITY=+1.)
           (62-SM-154,E-LVL2=0.544,SPIN=6.,PARITY=+1.)
ENDBIB               9
COMMON               2          3
EN         ANG
MEV        ADEG
        26.       135.
ENDCOMMON            3
DATA                 4          4
E-LVL1     E-LVL2     DATA       DATA-ERR
MEV        MEV        MB/SR      MB/SR
         0.      0.082       7.67       0.68
         0.      0.267       1.37       0.14
         0.      0.544      0.114      0.026
